   <p begin="00:20:55.421" end="00:20:56.589" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ゼニガメ）ゼニゼニー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:20:56.673" end="00:20:59.467" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ハルカ）あっ ゼニガメ<br />また勝手に…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:20:59.842" end="00:21:00.843" style="s1"><span style="s2">ゼニゼニー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:21:00.927" end="00:21:02.136" style="s1"><span style="s2">（一同）えっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:21:02.220" end="00:21:03.346" style="s1"><span style="s2">わあ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:21:10.311" end="00:21:11.479" style="s1"><span style="s2">（マサト）すごいや</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:21:11.562" end="00:21:15.024" style="s1"><span style="s2">（タケシ）バルビートたちが<br />求愛のダンスを踊ってるんだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:21:15.108" end="00:21:16.651" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）きれいだな</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:21:16.734" end="00:21:17.568" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ピカチュウ）ピ～カ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:21:18.236" end="00:21:23.950" style="s1"><span style="s2">ハルカちゃん 私たちはあれを<br />幸せの光と呼んでるのよ</span></p> 
